{"tid":2274682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國第51個州 - Puerto Rico","createTime":"2020-11-06T14:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T15:46:38.000Z","uid":121784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e7dc3ce51289eba8136f0d2919118981ffefb370","tid":2274682,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"係美國大選既同一日, 美國&quot;自治領土&quot; Puerto Rico舉行了公投, 決定應否成為美國其中一州<br />\n<br />\n同美國大選一樣, 點票仲未完, 但支持成為美國一州暫時領先<br />\n<br />\n最終決定權係美國國會. 民主黨較支持, 而共和黨就有所保留, 因為Puerto Rico上Hispanic佔多數, 而傳統上Hispanic較支持民主黨 (但今次Florida, 某程度上靠Hispanic, 保住共和黨)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://elecciones2020.ceepur.org/Noche_del_Evento_92/index.html#en/default/PLEBISCITO_Resumen.xml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felecciones2020.ceepur.org%2FNoche_del_Evento_92%2Findex.html%23en%2Fdefault%2FPLEBISCITO_Resumen.xml&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9uSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=739f42d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://elecciones2020.ceepur.org/Noche_del_Evento_92/index.html#en/default/PLEBISCITO_Resumen.xml</a>"},{"pid":"dd5d81e9b75f68a684be2c55c5bc260f6659f8e6","tid":2274682,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"民主黨鬼敢真係咁做，波多黎各既民主共和兩黨勢力大致平衡，民主黨優勢好細，多個搖擺州對佢地既利益有潛在影響"},{"pid":"a9f9c2ce163308271ff72c014754fe9dcbfefc75","tid":2274682,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"而且波多黎各年輕人口流失率大，宜家就話建州所以傾民主黨，真係建州成功後就未別了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea81bff87d21c914ec87fee480f9c14b0e5c712","tid":2274682,"uid":313546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"真戰鬥民族 日後打仗都靠佢地 有得入好入"},{"pid":"1b41ceee4c6598a4eca798f6b1b518eb3b05ddb2","tid":2274682,"uid":8257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a9f9c2ce163308271ff72c014754fe9dcbfefc75","tid